{"tid":2074760,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"黃遠輝：即使入息中位數升 居屋仍維持市價六三折出售","createTime":"2020-06-22T10:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T14:44:39.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac113436163c54655f36dd47a285783d848063f6","tid":2074760,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"黃遠輝：即使入息中位數升 居屋仍維持市價六三折出售<br />\n2020-06-22 HKT 18:36<br />\n<br />\n房委會資助房屋小組通過出售新一期居屋，4個屋苑共提供7047個單位，另加18個上期無完成銷售合約的單位，即合共有7065個單位，將以市價的六三折發售，單位價錢介乎123萬至513萬元，並會視乎4至6月非業主住戶的入息中位數，再敲定最終折扣率和售價。<br />\n<br />\n小組委員會主席黃遠輝表示，即使入息中位數上升，售價都會保持在市價六三折的水平，不會調整相關折扣。他說，有關做法是因應疫情而作出的臨時折扣率，在會議上，委員對此做法表示讚賞。他又說，委員對疫情的影響有不同看法，有委員覺得樓價可能下跌，亦有委員覺得見到樓市有承托，可能會上升。 <br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533456-20200622.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533456-20200622.htm&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=f5bf03cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533456-20200622.htm&h=0311ed29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533456-20200622.htm</a>"},{"pid":"166f7583b4afd90b0ea3aeb5c1b9149dca0eb02f","tid":2074760,"uid":51369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"市價升得快過入息中位數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af293ce9afda6d7ddfba25c690bc42d04fbcb9b","tid":2074760,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"關愛座都2100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee3fa714cc534e0ef8afeed5b6f4de3f8337f44","tid":2074760,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"一人都有700<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5591e9d